Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:04.310
I am Nikolai Amosov.

00:00:04.310 --> 00:00:07.319
Born in 1913 in Olkhovo, Russia.

00:00:07.319 --> 00:00:12.250
I am a Soviet and Ukrainian doctor of Russian
origin, heart surgeon, inventor, best-selling

00:00:12.250 --> 00:00:16.840
author, and exercise enthusiast, known for
my inventions of several surgical procedures

00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:18.750
for treating heart defects.

00:00:18.750 --> 00:00:23.179
I completed my studies at the Cherepovets
College of Mechanics, the Arkhangelsk Medical

00:00:23.179 --> 00:00:27.720
Institute, and, by correspondence, the Soviet
Industrial Institute.

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:32.689
After the second world war, I moved to Kyiv
and in 1965 wrote my book “The Thoughts

00:00:32.689 --> 00:00:35.310
and the Heart”, selling millions of copies.

00:00:35.310 --> 00:00:37.600
I was the recipient of multiple awards.

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:43.079
I am a corresponding member of the Academy
of Medical Sciences of the USSR and Ukraine.

00:00:43.079 --> 00:00:48.719
From 1952 to 1983, I was the director of the
thoracic and heart surgery clinic at the Kyiv

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:53.480
Scientific Research Institute for Tubercular
Heart and Artery Surgery, becoming the institute’s

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:59.449
assistant director in 1968 and serving as
director from 1983 to 1988.

00:00:59.449 --> 00:01:04.260
In 1955 I founded the first heart surgery
clinic in Ukraine, which later became the

00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:07.150
Kyiv Institute of Cardiovascular Surgery.

00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:11.840
I was also a founder of the Ukrainian school
of biological, medical, and psychological

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:13.210
cybernetics.

00:01:13.210 --> 00:01:17.610
I am the author of more than 400 scholarly
works and 19 monographs, which include an

00:01:17.610 --> 00:01:22.460
outline of thoracic surgery, a guide to surgery
for heart defects, and a study of algorithms

00:01:22.460 --> 00:01:23.620
of the mind.

00:01:23.620 --> 00:01:28.500
I was the recipient of multiple orders including
the Hero of Socialist Labor title, two Orders

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:33.260
of Lenin, the Order of the Patriotic War,
two Orders of the Red Star, and the Lenin

00:01:33.260 --> 00:01:34.920
Prize.

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:39.610
In 2008 I was recognized as second after Yaroslav
I the Wise among the Great Ukrainians by a

00:01:39.610 --> 00:01:43.780
public poll conducted for the TV show named
The Greatest Ukrainians.

00:01:43.780 --> 00:01:48.390
By the order of the Cabinet of Ministers of
Ukraine, the Institute of Cardiovascular Surgery

00:01:48.390 --> 00:01:52.460
of the Academy of Medical Sciences of Ukraine
was named after me.

00:01:52.460 --> 00:01:57.040
Streets in Kyiv were named after me and the
National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine established

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:01.570
the Nikolai Amosov Prize which is awarded
for significant scientific works.

00:02:01.570 --> 00:02:04.090
The human body is a marvelous masterpiece.

00:02:04.090 --> 00:02:04.751
Please take care of it.

